## PROJECT CONTEXT

### What is MMS?
Metro Mileage Management System - High-performance visualization for railway
fleet maintenance planning. Core UX: "Semantic Zoom" (Google Earth-style).
Performance target: 60fps with 50+ trains, 10 years of data.

### Client
Dubai Metro / Keolis MHI
- 128 trains (79 Alstom + 49 Kinki Sharyo)
- 2 depots: Al Rashidiya (Red), Jebel Ali (Green)
- 12-year contract

### Tech Stack (V1.0)
- React 18.3.1 + Vite 5.x
- React Three Fiber 8.x + drei 9.x + three 0.170.x
- BlueprintJS 6.1.0 (PatternFly deferred to V1.1)
- @zazcart/tools (state management)

